1. Copy the directory antor-beamer somewhere in your texmf tree, e.g.

on linux, you can install it e.g. in:
    /usr/share/texmf/tex/latex/beamer/themes/

on windows:
    somewhere in a miktex folder...

2. Refresh the file name database

on linux, in a terminal:
    sudo texhash

on windows, click on "refresh FNDB" in the MikTeX settings manager
